# UI / Component context

Editing UI. See docs/CODING_STANDARDS.md §2, §4, §8

## Quick checks

- Use Next.js `<Image>` for images
- Tailwind only, no inline styles
- Semantic HTML, a11y (alt, focus-visible)
- Layout: section `w-full`, content `mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8`
- Interactive states: hover, active, disabled, focus-visible
